The '''Blackstone Wind Farm''' is an approved offshore wind power project in the [[Black Sea]] area of [[Romania]]. It will have 100 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ziarulring.ro/stiri/ne_facem_parc_eolian_in_marea_neagra.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303212605/http://www.ziarulring.ro/stiri/ne_facem_parc_eolian_in_marea_neagra.html|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2016-03-03|title=Ne facem parc eolian în Marea Neagră|date=2009-07-23|publisher=www.ziarulring.ro|language=Romanian|accessdate=2009-07-30}} </ref> with a nominal output of around 5 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] each which will deliver up to 500 MW of power, enough to power over 334,821 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$1.4 billion.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ziare.com/Peste_1_miliard_de_euro_vor_fi_investiti_de_Blackstone_intr_un_parc_eoli-358852.html|title=Peste 1 miliard de euro vor fi investiti de Blackstone intr-un parc eolian marin|date=2009-07-15|publisher=www.ziare.com|language=Romanian|accessdate=2009-07-30}}</ref>

