eli Dam''' is an [[embankment dam]], currently under construction near the town of Laleli on the [[Çoruh River]] in [[Erzurum Province]], Turkey. The primary purpose of the dam is [[hydroelectric]] power production. After a prolonged legal battle, construction on the dam began in 2013 and it is expected to be complete in 2017. The dam, which will power a 99 MW power station, will also flood several villages to include Laleli. The dam's reservoir will stretch east into [[Bayburt Province]].<ref>{{cite web|title=BİZLERE SAHİP ÇIKILMAZ İSE BAYBURT KAYBEDER|url=http://www.bayburtmedya.com/index.php/bmgundem/item/1060-bizlere-sahip-%C3%A7ikilmaz-ise-bayburt-kaybeder|publisher=Bayburt Medya|accessdate=10 May 2013|date=12 March 2013}}</ref>
