The '''Naturmobil''' is a [[horse]]-powered vehicle for travel on paved [[road]]s.<ref Name="autoworld">{{cite web | last = | first = | authorlink = | coauthors = | title = Naturmobil: Car runs on realy (sic) 'horse power'! | publisher = It's your auto world | date = May 5, 2008 | url = http://autoworld.wordpress.com/2008/05/05/naturmobil-car-runs-on-realy-%E2%80%98horse-power%E2%80%99/ | doi = | accessdate = 2008-05-08 }}</ref><ref Name="Dharmarajan">{{cite web | last =Dharmarajan | first =Subramani | authorlink = | coauthors = | title =Naturmobil: Cart runs on ‘horse power’ | publisher =Xpress News | date =May 1, 2008<!--, 08:54 -->| url =http://www.xpress4me.com/news/uae/dubai/20007183.html | doi = | accessdate = 2008-05-08 }}</ref> The vehicle is controlled by a driver in a similar way to a motor-driven vehicle, with the horse inside the vehicle on a [[treadmill]]. It weighs {{Convert|300|kg|lb|abbr=on}}, or probably around {{Convert|700|kg|lb|abbr=on}} with the horse. It cruises at about {{Convert|20|km/h|mph|abbr=on}}, with a top speed of about {{Convert|80|km/h|mph|abbr=on}}. The treadmill also charges [[battery (electricity)|batteries]] which will power the vehicle if the horse needs a break.<ref Name="Dharmarajan"/><ref Name="Safford">{{cite web | last =Safford | first =Matt | authorlink = | coauthors = | title =Naturmobil Horse Car Takes Horse Power to New Low | publisher =Gearlog | date =May 7, 2008 | url =http://www.gearlog.com/2008/05/naturmobil_horse_car_takes_hor.php | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20091215013730/http://www.gearlog.com/2008/05/naturmobil_horse_car_takes_hor.php | archivedate =December 15, 2009 | doi = | accessdate = 2008-05-08 }}</ref>
The vehicle was invented by [[Abdolhadi Mirhejazi]], an Iranian engineer, who says "the Naturemobil was developed with the safety and welfare of the animal in mind".<ref name="autoworld"/> At least one [[veterinarian]], Dr. Matt Pietrak, has concerns for the horse's wellbeing while powering the vehicle.<ref Name="McLennan">{{cite web |last = McLennan |first = Paul |authorlink = |coauthors = |title = Vet bridles at truck |publisher = 7days |date = |url = http://www.7days.ae/en/2008/05/05/vet-bridles-at-truck.html |doi = |accessdate = 2008-05-08 }}{{dead link|date=February 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>
