ydroelectric]] power generation and it will support a 636.6 MW [[hydroelectric]] power station. The {{Convert|150|m|ft|abbr=on}} tall dam will withhold a reservoir of {{Convert|783800000|m3|acre.ft|abbr=on}}. It is owned by Kalehan Energy Generation.<ref>{{cite web|title=Upper Kalekoy Dam and HEPP|url=http://www.kalehan.com.tr/en/projects/yukari-kalekoy-dam-and-hepp.html|publisher=Kalehan Energy Group|accessdate=3 March 2016}}</ref>
